A4.text: The Dannebrog holds the Guinness world record of being the oldest continuously used national flag, that is since 1625.

A5.text: The Dannebrog (Danish: Dannebrog, pronounced [ˈtænəˌpʁoˀ]) is the flag of Denmark.
